    "Both stations need to be served by the same transit network. Try picking stations that share a metro, tram or bus line.": {
      "comment": "A description of the error that occurs when the start and end stations of a ticket are not in the same public transport network.",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Beide Stationen müssen vom selben Verkehrsnetz bedient werden. Wählen Sie Stationen, die eine U-Bahn-, Tram- oder Buslinie teilen."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "These stations aren’t on the same network. Pick two that share a metro, tram, or bus line."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ambas estaciones deben pertenecer a la misma red de transporte. Prueba con estaciones que compartan una línea de metro, tranvía o autobús."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Les deux stations doivent appartenir au même réseau de transport. Choisissez des stations partageant une ligne de métro, de tram ou de bus."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Entrambe le stazioni devono appartenere alla stessa rete di trasporti. Prova a scegliere stazioni che condividono una linea di metro, tram o autobus."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "両方の駅は同じ交通ネットワークに属している必要があります。地下鉄、トラム、バスのいずれかの路線を共有する駅を選んでください。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "두 역은 같은 교통 네트워크에 속해야 합니다. 같은 지하철, 트램 또는 버스 노선을 공유하는 역을 선택해 보세요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "两个车站需在同一交通网络内。请选择共享地铁、有轨电车或公交线路的车站。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
