    "Each category has different templates that match it. You can also check the content of each template by tapping the information button.": {
      "comment": "Tip shown in onboarding when picking a ticket template.",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Jede Kategorie hat passende Vorlagen. Tippen Sie auf das Info-Symbol, um den Inhalt jeder Vorlage anzusehen."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Every category has its own templates. Tap the info icon on a template to see what it needs."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cada categoría tiene plantillas distintas que la acompañan. Toca el botón de información para ver el contenido de cada una."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Chaque catégorie dispose de modèles qui lui correspondent. Touchez le bouton d'information pour voir le contenu de chaque modèle."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ogni categoria ha modelli specifici. Tocca il pulsante info per vedere il contenuto di ogni modello."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "各カテゴリには対応するテンプレートが用意されています。情報ボタンをタップすると各テンプレートの内容を確認できます。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "각 카테고리에는 어울리는 템플릿이 있습니다. 정보 버튼을 누르면 템플릿별 내용을 확인할 수 있습니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "每个类别都有相应的模板。点按信息按钮可查看每个模板的内容。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Each category has its own set of designs — Afterglow, Studio, Terminal, Heritage, Prism for planes; Express, Orient, Night for trains. Pick the one that matches the moment.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Jede Kategorie hat ihre eigenen Designs – Afterglow, Studio, Terminal, Heritage, Prism für Flugzeuge; Express, Orient, Night für Züge. Wählen Sie das, was zum Moment passt."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Each category has its own designs. Pick the one that matches the moment."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cada categoría tiene sus propios diseños — Afterglow, Studio, Terminal, Heritage, Prism para aviones; Express, Orient, Night para trenes. Elige el que mejor encaje con el momento."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Chaque catégorie a ses propres designs — Afterglow, Studio, Terminal, Heritage, Prism pour les avions ; Express, Orient, Night pour les trains. Choisissez celui qui correspond au moment."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ogni categoria ha i propri design — Afterglow, Studio, Terminal, Heritage, Prism per gli aerei; Express, Orient, Night per i treni. Scegli quello che si adatta al momento."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "各カテゴリには独自のデザインが用意されています — 飛行機用にAfterglow、Studio、Terminal、Heritage、Prism。電車用にExpress、Orient、Night。その瞬間に合うものを選びましょう。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "카테고리마다 디자인이 다릅니다 — 비행기는 Afterglow, Studio, Terminal, Heritage, Prism, 기차는 Express, Orient, Night. 순간에 맞는 디자인을 고르세요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "每个类别都有专属设计 —— 飞机有 Afterglow、Studio、Terminal、Heritage、Prism；火车有 Express、Orient、Night。挑一个符合当下心情的。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
