        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "仅限早期使用者"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Early adopters can use all the features available in Lumoria. You will be automatically opted in for feedback on the product as it is being built (surveys, rare interview requests).": {
      "comment": "A description of the benefits of being an early adopter.",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Early Adopter können alle in Lumoria verfügbaren Funktionen nutzen. Sie werden automatisch in Feedback-Aktionen während der Entwicklung des Produkts einbezogen (Umfragen, gelegentliche Interview-Anfragen)."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Early adopters get the full app, plus the occasional survey or interview request as we build."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Los early adopters pueden usar todas las funciones de Lumoria. Te incluiremos automáticamente en las consultas sobre el producto a medida que avanza (encuestas, solicitudes ocasionales de entrevistas)."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Les early adopters peuvent utiliser toutes les fonctionnalités disponibles dans Lumoria. Vous serez automatiquement inscrit pour donner votre avis sur le produit en cours de développement (sondages, demandes d'entretien occasionnelles)."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Gli early adopter possono usare tutte le funzionalità disponibili in Lumoria. Verrai incluso automaticamente nelle iniziative di feedback sul prodotto durante lo sviluppo (sondaggi, occasionali richieste di intervista)."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "アーリーアダプターはLumoriaのすべての機能を利用できます。プロダクト開発中のフィードバック（アンケートやごくまれなインタビュー依頼）に自動的に登録されます。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "얼리어답터는 Lumoria의 모든 기능을 사용할 수 있습니다. 제품 개발 중 피드백(설문, 드문 인터뷰 요청)에 자동으로 참여하게 됩니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "早期使用者可以使用 Lumoria 的全部功能。在产品开发过程中，您将被自动纳入反馈环节（问卷调查、偶尔的访谈邀请）。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Early adopters help build Lumoria for everyone else by participating in research to improve the app and helping build a better app.": {
      "comment": "A description of the benefits of being an early adopter.",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Early Adopter helfen, Lumoria für alle anderen mitzugestalten, indem sie an Studien zur Verbesserung der App teilnehmen und beim Aufbau einer besseren App mithelfen."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Early adopters shape Lumoria. Your feedback helps us build a better app for everyone."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Los early adopters ayudan a construir Lumoria para los demás participando en investigaciones para mejorar la app."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Les early adopters aident à construire Lumoria pour tout le monde en participant à la recherche pour améliorer l'application."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Gli early adopter aiutano a costruire Lumoria per tutti gli altri partecipando alla ricerca per migliorare l'app."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "アーリーアダプターはアプリ改善のためのリサーチに参加し、より良いLumoriaを皆のために作る手助けをします。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "얼리어답터는 앱 개선을 위한 리서치에 참여해 모두를 위한 Lumoria를 함께 만들어갑니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "早期使用者通过参与研究来帮助打造更好的 Lumoria。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
