    "Every field is optional. Fill in only what matters to you — airline, flight number, origin and destination, date, seat, gate.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Jedes Feld ist optional. Füllen Sie nur das aus, was für Sie wichtig ist – Fluggesellschaft, Flugnummer, Start- und Zielort, Datum, Platz, Gate."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Every field is optional. Fill in only what matters to you."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cada campo es opcional. Rellena solo lo que te importe — aerolínea, número de vuelo, origen y destino, fecha, asiento, puerta."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Chaque champ est optionnel. Ne remplissez que ce qui compte pour vous — compagnie, numéro de vol, départ et arrivée, date, siège, porte."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ogni campo è facoltativo. Compila solo ciò che ti interessa — compagnia, numero di volo, origine e destinazione, data, posto, gate."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "すべての項目は任意です。あなたにとって大切な項目だけを入力してください — 航空会社、便名、出発地と目的地、日付、座席、ゲート。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "모든 항목은 선택입니다. 중요한 것만 입력하세요 — 항공사, 편명, 출발지와 도착지, 날짜, 좌석, 게이트."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "每个字段都是可选项。只填写对你重要的内容 —— 航司、航班号、出发与到达、日期、座位、登机口。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Every Lumoria ticket starts as a blank canvas. Pick a kind, choose a look, fill in the details — done.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Jedes Lumoria-Ticket beginnt als leere Leinwand. Wählen Sie eine Art, einen Look und tragen Sie die Details ein – fertig."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "Every Lumoria ticket starts as a blank canvas. Pick a kind, choose a look, fill in the details — done."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cada boleto de Lumoria empieza como un lienzo en blanco. Elige el tipo, el estilo y rellena los datos — listo."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Chaque billet Lumoria commence par une toile vierge. Choisissez un type, un style, remplissez les détails — c'est tout."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ogni biglietto Lumoria parte come una tela bianca. Scegli un tipo, un look, compila i dettagli — fatto."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "すべてのLumoriaチケットは白紙のキャンバスから始まります。種類とルックを選び、詳細を入力するだけ。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "모든 Lumoria 티켓은 빈 캔버스에서 시작합니다. 종류와 스타일을 고르고 세부 정보를 채우면 끝."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "每张 Lumoria 票券都从一张空白画布开始。选种类、挑外观、填详情 —— 就这么简单。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Every template have specific information attached to it. Fill all the required information to edit your ticket.": {
      "comment": "Tip shown on the onboarding screen when the user is filling out a ticket.",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Jede Vorlage enthält bestimmte Informationen. Füllen Sie alle erforderlichen Felder aus, um Ihr Ticket zu bearbeiten."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Each template needs a few key details. Fill them in to keep editing."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cada plantilla tiene información concreta asociada. Rellena todos los datos requeridos para editar tu boleto."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Chaque modèle est associé à des informations spécifiques. Remplissez tous les champs requis pour modifier votre billet."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ogni modello ha informazioni specifiche. Compila tutti i campi richiesti per modificare il biglietto."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "テンプレートごとに必要な情報が決まっています。チケットを編集するには、必須項目をすべて入力してください。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "템플릿마다 필요한 정보가 다릅니다. 필수 항목을 모두 채워 티켓을 편집하세요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "每个模板都有专属信息。请填写所有必填项以编辑你的票券。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Every ticket you make in Lumoria becomes an iMessage sticker, automatically. No extra step, no export.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Jedes Ticket, das Sie in Lumoria erstellen, wird automatisch zum iMessage-Sticker. Kein zusätzlicher Schritt, kein Export."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "Every ticket you make in Lumoria becomes an iMessage sticker, automatically. No extra step, no export."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cada boleto que creas en Lumoria se convierte automáticamente en un sticker de iMessage. Sin pasos extra, sin exportación."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Chaque billet que vous créez dans Lumoria devient automatiquement un sticker iMessage. Aucune étape supplémentaire, aucun export."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ogni biglietto creato in Lumoria diventa automaticamente uno sticker iMessage. Nessun passaggio in più, nessuna esportazione."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lumoriaで作成したすべてのチケットは自動的にiMessageステッカーになります。追加の操作も書き出しも不要です。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lumoria에서 만든 모든 티켓은 자동으로 iMessage 스티커가 됩니다. 별도의 단계나 내보내기가 필요 없습니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "你在 Lumoria 创建的每张票券都会自动变成 iMessage 贴纸。无需额外步骤，无需导出。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Every ticket you save lives in All tickets — your full gallery of moments.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Jedes gespeicherte Ticket finden Sie in „Alle Tickets“ – Ihre komplette Galerie der Momente."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Every ticket you save lives in All tickets — your gallery of moments."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cada boleto que guardas vive en Todos los boletos — tu galería completa de momentos."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Chaque billet enregistré vit dans Tous les billets — votre galerie complète de moments."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ogni biglietto salvato vive in Tutti i biglietti — la tua galleria completa di momenti."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "保存したすべてのチケットは「すべてのチケット」に集まります — モーメントのギャラリーです。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "저장한 모든 티켓은 모든 티켓에 보관됩니다 — 순간들의 갤러리입니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "保存的每张票券都在“全部票券”中 —— 你完整的瞬间画廊。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Every ticket you've made is already in this memory.": {
