        }
      }
    },
    "If %@ has an account, we've sent a reset link.": {
      "comment": "Forgot password — alert body. %@ is the user's email address.",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Falls %@ ein Konto hat, ist der Reset-Link unterwegs."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "If %@ has an account, the reset link is on its way."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Si %@ tiene una cuenta, el enlace de restablecimiento ya va en camino."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Si %@ a un compte, le lien de réinitialisation est en route."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Se %@ ha un account, il link di reset è in arrivo."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "%@ のアカウントがあれば、リセットリンクをお送りしています。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "%@ 계정이 있다면, 재설정 링크가 곧 도착해요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "如果 %@ 已注册，重置链接已经在路上。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If something doesn't read cleanly, tap Fill manually — Lumoria will keep whatever it managed to pull, and you can finish the rest by hand.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Wenn etwas nicht sauber ausgelesen wird, tippen Sie auf Manuell ausfüllen – Lumoria behält, was es erfassen konnte, und Sie können den Rest von Hand ergänzen."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "If something doesn’t import cleanly, tap Fill manually. We’ll keep what we have — you finish the rest."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Si algo no se lee bien, toca Rellenar manualmente — Lumoria conservará lo que haya podido extraer y tú completas el resto a mano."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Si quelque chose n'est pas bien lu, touchez Remplir manuellement — Lumoria conserve ce qu'il a pu extraire, et vous terminez le reste à la main."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Se qualcosa non viene letto correttamente, tocca Compila manualmente — Lumoria conserva ciò che è riuscito a estrarre e tu completi il resto a mano."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "うまく読み取れない場合は「手動で入力」をタップしてください — Lumoriaは取得できた分を保持し、残りはご自身で入力できます。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "내용이 잘 인식되지 않으면 수동 입력을 누르세요 — Lumoria가 인식한 내용은 유지되고, 나머지는 직접 채울 수 있습니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "如果识别不清，请点按“手动填写” —— Lumoria 会保留已识别的部分，你手动补全其余内容。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If you decide to revoke your early adopter status, you will return back to the original limit of 3 memories and 10 tickets per account.": {
      "comment": "A description of the consequences of revoking an early adopter status.",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Wenn Sie Ihren Early-Adopter-Status widerrufen, kehren Sie zur ursprünglichen Grenze von 3 Erinnerungen und 10 Tickets pro Konto zurück."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Revoke your early adopter status and you’ll go back to 3 memories and 10 tickets per account."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Si decides revocar tu estado de early adopter, volverás al límite original de 3 recuerdos y 10 boletos por cuenta."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Si vous décidez de révoquer votre statut d'early adopter, vous reviendrez à la limite initiale de 3 souvenirs et 10 billets par compte."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Se decidi di revocare lo stato di early adopter, tornerai al limite originale di 3 ricordi e 10 biglietti per account."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "アーリーアダプターのステータスを取り消すと、アカウントごとに思い出3件・チケット10枚という元の制限に戻ります。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "얼리어답터 상태를 철회하면 계정당 추억 3개, 티켓 10개의 원래 제한으로 돌아갑니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "如果您撤销早期使用者状态，将恢复每账户 3 个回忆和 10 张票券的原始限制。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If you haven't canceled, your subscription will begin and you will be charged.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Wenn Sie nicht kündigen, beginnt Ihr Abonnement und es wird Ihnen eine Gebühr berechnet."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "If you haven’t cancelled, your subscription starts and you’ll be charged."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Si no has cancelado, tu suscripción comenzará y se te cobrará."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Si vous n'avez pas annulé, votre abonnement commencera et vous serez facturé."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Se non hai annullato, il tuo abbonamento partirà e verrà addebitato il costo."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "キャンセルしない場合、サブスクリプションが開始し、料金が請求されます。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "취소하지 않으면 구독이 시작되고 요금이 청구됩니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "若未取消，您的订阅将开始并扣款。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If your boarding pass is already in Apple Wallet, Lumoria can read it and fill in the details for you.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Wenn Ihre Bordkarte bereits in Apple Wallet liegt, kann Lumoria sie lesen und die Details für Sie eintragen."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "If your boarding pass is already in Apple Wallet, Lumoria can read it and fill in the details for you."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Si tu tarjeta de embarque ya está en Apple Wallet, Lumoria puede leerla y rellenar los datos por ti."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Si votre carte d'embarquement est déjà dans Apple Wallet, Lumoria peut la lire et remplir les détails pour vous."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Se la tua carta d'imbarco è già in Apple Wallet, Lumoria può leggerla e compilare i dettagli al posto tuo."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "搭乗券がすでにApple Walletにある場合、Lumoriaがそれを読み取って詳細を入力します。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "탑승권이 이미 Apple Wallet에 있다면 Lumoria가 이를 읽어 세부 정보를 채워드립니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "如果您的登机牌已存于 Apple Wallet，Lumoria 可读取并自动填入详情。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If your gallery is still empty, you'll see the seven-point star and a gentle nudge — your gallery starts with one tap.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Wenn Ihre Galerie noch leer ist, sehen Sie den siebenzackigen Stern und einen sanften Hinweis – Ihre Galerie beginnt mit einem Tipp."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "An empty gallery shows the seven-point star — your first ticket is one tap away."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Si tu galería aún está vacía, verás la estrella de siete puntas y una invitación suave — tu galería empieza con un toque."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Si votre galerie est encore vide, vous verrez l'étoile à sept branches et une invitation douce — votre galerie commence en un geste."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Se la tua galleria è ancora vuota, vedrai la stella a sette punte e un invito gentile — la tua galleria parte con un tocco."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ギャラリーがまだ空の場合、7つ星のマークとやさしい案内が表示されます — ギャラリーはタップひとつで始まります。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "갤러리가 비어 있으면 7각 별 모양과 부드러운 안내가 보입니다 — 한 번의 터치로 갤러리가 시작됩니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "如果你的画廊还空着，你会看到七角星和一句温柔提示 —— 一键即可开始你的画廊。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
