    "iOS brings up the share sheet. Tap Messages, WhatsApp, Telegram, Signal, Messenger, Discord — whichever one the moment belongs in.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "iOS öffnet das Teilen-Menü. Tippen Sie auf Nachrichten, WhatsApp, Telegram, Signal, Messenger, Discord – je nachdem, wohin der Moment gehört."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "iOS brings up the share sheet. Tap Messages, WhatsApp, Telegram, Signal, Messenger, Discord — whichever one the moment belongs in."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "iOS abre el menú de compartir. Toca Mensajes, WhatsApp, Telegram, Signal, Messenger o Discord — el que mejor le siente al momento."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "iOS ouvre la feuille de partage. Touchez Messages, WhatsApp, Telegram, Signal, Messenger, Discord — celle qui correspond au moment."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "iOS apre il foglio di condivisione. Tocca Messaggi, WhatsApp, Telegram, Signal, Messenger, Discord — quello adatto al momento."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "iOSの共有シートが表示されます。「メッセージ」「WhatsApp」「Telegram」「Signal」「Messenger」「Discord」など、その瞬間にふさわしいものをタップします。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "iOS의 공유 시트가 열립니다. 메시지, WhatsApp, Telegram, Signal, Messenger, Discord 등 그 순간에 어울리는 곳을 누르세요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "iOS 弹出分享菜单。点按信息、WhatsApp、Telegram、Signal、Messenger、Discord —— 哪一个适合当下的心情就用哪个。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
