    "Once you will have tickets added to this memory, they will appear on this tile. Tap this memory to open it.": {
      "comment": "Text displayed in a tip when a memory is created.",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Sobald Sie Tickets zu dieser Erinnerung hinzugefügt haben, erscheinen sie auf dieser Kachel. Tippen Sie auf die Erinnerung, um sie zu öffnen."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tickets you add show up on this tile. Tap to open the memory."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cuando añadas boletos a este recuerdo, aparecerán en esta ficha. Toca el recuerdo para abrirlo."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Une fois des billets ajoutés à ce souvenir, ils apparaîtront sur cette tuile. Touchez le souvenir pour l'ouvrir."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una volta aggiunti dei biglietti a questo ricordo, compariranno in questa tile. Tocca il ricordo per aprirlo."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "この思い出にチケットを追加すると、このタイルに表示されます。タップして開きます。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "이 추억에 티켓을 추가하면 타일에 표시됩니다. 추억을 눌러 열어보세요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "向此回忆添加票券后，它们会显示在此卡片上。点按回忆即可打开。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Once your benefit selected, you will not be able to modify it.": {
