    "Tap Delete ticket to let it go. The ticket disappears from your collection, your memories, and your iMessage sticker pack.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tippen Sie auf „Ticket löschen“, um es loszulassen. Das Ticket verschwindet aus Ihrer Sammlung, Ihren Erinnerungen und Ihrem iMessage-Sticker-Pack."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tap Delete ticket to let it go. It’ll leave your gallery, memories, and sticker pack."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Toca Eliminar boleto para dejarlo ir. El boleto desaparece de tu colección, tus recuerdos y tu pack de stickers de iMessage."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Touchez Supprimer le billet pour le laisser partir. Le billet disparaît de votre collection, de vos souvenirs et de votre pack de stickers iMessage."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tocca Elimina biglietto per lasciarlo andare. Il biglietto scompare dalla tua collezione, dai tuoi ricordi e dal pacchetto sticker iMessage."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "「チケットを削除」をタップして手放します。チケットはコレクション、思い出、iMessageステッカーパックから消えます。"
