            "value": "점 세 개(•••)를 누른 다음 내보내기…를 선택하세요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "点按省略号（•••），然后选择导出…"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tap the link we sent to %@ to activate your account, then log in.": {
      "comment": "A message in a sheet that appears when the user has not yet verified their email. The argument is the email address that needs to be verified.",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tippen Sie auf den Link, den wir an %@ gesendet haben, um Ihr Konto zu aktivieren, und melden Sie sich anschließend an."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tap the link we sent to %@ to activate your account, then sign in."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Toca el enlace que enviamos a %@ para activar tu cuenta y luego inicia sesión."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Touchez le lien que nous avons envoyé à %@ pour activer votre compte, puis connectez-vous."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tocca il link che abbiamo inviato a %@ per attivare l'account, poi accedi."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "%@ に送信したリンクをタップしてアカウントを有効化し、ログインしてください。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "%@(으)로 보낸 링크를 눌러 계정을 활성화한 다음 로그인하세요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "点按我们发送到 %@ 的链接以激活您的账户，然后登录。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tap the link we sent to %@ to activate your account, then log in. Check your spam folder if you don't see it.": {
      "comment": "A message in an alert that appears when the user taps the \"Resend email\" button in the \"Verify your email\" alert. The argument is the user's email address.",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tippen Sie auf den Link, den wir an %@ gesendet haben, um Ihr Konto zu aktivieren, und melden Sie sich anschließend an. Schauen Sie im Spam-Ordner nach, falls Sie ihn nicht finden."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tap the link we sent to %@ to activate your account, then log in. Check spam if it didn’t land."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Toca el enlace que enviamos a %@ para activar tu cuenta y luego inicia sesión. Revisa la carpeta de spam si no lo ves."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Touchez le lien que nous avons envoyé à %@ pour activer votre compte, puis connectez-vous. Vérifiez vos courriers indésirables si vous ne le voyez pas."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tocca il link che abbiamo inviato a %@ per attivare l'account, poi accedi. Controlla la cartella spam se non lo trovi."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "%@ に送信したリンクをタップしてアカウントを有効化し、ログインしてください。見当たらない場合は迷惑メールフォルダをご確認ください。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "%@(으)로 보낸 링크를 눌러 계정을 활성화한 다음 로그인하세요. 보이지 않으면 스팸함을 확인하세요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "点按我们发送到 %@ 的链接以激活您的账户，然后登录。若未看到邮件，请检查垃圾邮件文件夹。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tap the memory you would like to add your ticket to. This can be changed later.": {
      "comment": "Tip to show when onboarding the Add to Memory sheet.",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tippen Sie auf die Erinnerung, zu der Sie Ihr Ticket hinzufügen möchten. Sie können dies später ändern."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pick a memory for this ticket. You can move it later."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Toca el recuerdo al que quieras añadir tu boleto. Esto se puede cambiar más tarde."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Touchez le souvenir auquel vous souhaitez ajouter votre billet. Vous pourrez le modifier plus tard."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tocca il ricordo a cui vuoi aggiungere il biglietto. Puoi modificarlo in seguito."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "チケットを追加したい思い出をタップしてください。あとで変更できます。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "티켓을 추가할 추억을 누르세요. 나중에 변경할 수 있습니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "点按想要添加票券的回忆。稍后可更改。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tap the sort icon and pick Sort by date, Sort by category, or Remove sorting. A small dot on the icon tells you when a sort is active.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tippen Sie auf das Sortier-Symbol und wählen Sie „Nach Datum sortieren“, „Nach Kategorie sortieren“ oder „Sortierung entfernen“. Ein kleiner Punkt auf dem Symbol zeigt an, dass eine Sortierung aktiv ist."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tap the sort icon to sort by date, category, or remove sorting. A dot on the icon means a sort is on."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Toca el icono de orden y elige Ordenar por fecha, Ordenar por categoría o Quitar orden. Un pequeño punto en el icono indica que el orden está activo."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Touchez l'icône de tri et choisissez Trier par date, Trier par catégorie ou Supprimer le tri. Un petit point sur l'icône indique qu'un tri est actif."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tocca l'icona dell'ordinamento e scegli Ordina per data, Ordina per categoria o Rimuovi ordinamento. Un piccolo puntino sull'icona indica che è attivo un ordinamento."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "並べ替えアイコンをタップして「日付順」「カテゴリ順」「並べ替えを解除」を選びます。アイコンの小さなドットは並べ替えが有効であることを示します。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "정렬 아이콘을 누르고 날짜순 정렬, 카테고리순 정렬 또는 정렬 해제를 선택하세요. 아이콘의 작은 점은 정렬이 활성화되어 있음을 알려줍니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "点按排序图标，选择按日期排序、按类别排序或取消排序。图标上的小圆点表示当前已启用排序。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tap the sticker icon, tap Cutout, and pick your ticket from the camera roll. Instagram lifts the ticket off the background and turns it into a sticker you can resize, rotate, and place anywhere.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tippen Sie auf das Sticker-Symbol, dann auf „Cutout“, und wählen Sie Ihr Ticket aus den Fotos. Instagram löst das Ticket aus dem Hintergrund und macht daraus einen Sticker, den Sie skalieren, drehen und überall platzieren können."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tap the sticker icon, then Cutout, and pick your ticket. Instagram lifts it off the background — resize, rotate, place anywhere."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Toca el icono de sticker, toca Recorte y elige tu boleto del carrete. Instagram saca el boleto del fondo y lo convierte en un sticker que puedes redimensionar, rotar y colocar donde quieras."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Touchez l'icône de sticker, touchez Découpe, puis choisissez votre billet dans la pellicule. Instagram détoure le billet de son fond et en fait un sticker que vous pouvez redimensionner, faire pivoter et placer où vous voulez."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tocca l'icona dello sticker, tocca Ritaglio e scegli il biglietto dal rullino. Instagram stacca il biglietto dallo sfondo e lo trasforma in uno sticker ridimensionabile, ruotabile e posizionabile ovunque."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ステッカーアイコンをタップして「カットアウト」を選び、カメラロールからチケットを選択します。Instagramがチケットを背景から切り抜き、サイズ変更・回転・自由な配置ができるステッカーに変えます。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "스티커 아이콘을 누르고 컷아웃을 누른 뒤 카메라 롤에서 티켓을 선택하세요. Instagram이 티켓을 배경에서 분리해 크기 조절, 회전, 자유 배치가 가능한 스티커로 만듭니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "点按贴纸图标，再点按抠图，从相册选择你的票券。Instagram 会把票券从背景中抠出，变成可缩放、旋转、随意摆放的贴纸。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
