            "value": "The Locket Tour"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The template and style stay locked to keep the design consistent. If you want a different look for the same journey, save a new ticket instead.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Vorlage und Stil bleiben gesperrt, damit das Design konsistent bleibt. Wenn Sie für dieselbe Reise einen anderen Look möchten, speichern Sie stattdessen ein neues Ticket."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Template and style stay locked to keep the design consistent. For a different look, save a new ticket."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "La plantilla y el estilo permanecen bloqueados para mantener un diseño coherente. Si quieres otro look para el mismo viaje, guarda un boleto nuevo."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Le modèle et le style restent verrouillés pour préserver la cohérence du design. Si vous voulez un autre look pour le même voyage, enregistrez plutôt un nouveau billet."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Modello e stile restano bloccati per mantenere un design coerente. Se vuoi un look diverso per lo stesso viaggio, salva un nuovo biglietto."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "デザインを一貫させるため、テンプレートとスタイルはロックされたままです。同じ旅で違うルックがほしい場合は、新しいチケットを保存してください。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "디자인 일관성을 위해 템플릿과 스타일은 잠겨 있습니다. 같은 여정에 다른 스타일을 원한다면 새 티켓을 저장하세요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "模板和风格保持锁定以保证设计一致。如果想给同一段旅程换个外观，请重新保存一张票券。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The ticket goes as a high-resolution image, alongside a short message you can edit before sending.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Das Ticket geht als hochauflösendes Bild raus, zusammen mit einer kurzen Nachricht, die Sie vor dem Senden anpassen können."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The ticket sends as a high-resolution image with a short message you can edit first."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "El boleto se envía como imagen de alta resolución, junto con un mensaje corto que puedes editar antes de enviar."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Le billet part sous forme d'image haute résolution, accompagné d'un court message que vous pouvez modifier avant l'envoi."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Il biglietto viene inviato come immagine ad alta risoluzione, insieme a un breve messaggio modificabile prima dell'invio."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "チケットは高解像度の画像と、送信前に編集できる短いメッセージとともに送られます。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "티켓은 고해상도 이미지와 함께, 보내기 전에 수정할 수 있는 짧은 메시지와 함께 전송됩니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "票券会以高分辨率图像发送，并附带一条可在发送前编辑的短消息。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The toggles below won't take effect until you enable notifications for Lumoria in iOS Settings. Tap to open.": {
      "comment": "A description of the effect of toggling notifications.",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Die untenstehenden Schalter wirken sich erst aus, wenn Sie Mitteilungen für Lumoria in den iOS-Einstellungen aktivieren. Tippen Sie zum Öffnen."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Turn on notifications for Lumoria in Settings first — the toggles below take effect after that. Tap to open."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Los interruptores de abajo no surtirán efecto hasta que actives las notificaciones de Lumoria en Ajustes de iOS. Toca para abrir."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Les interrupteurs ci-dessous ne prendront effet qu'après avoir activé les notifications pour Lumoria dans les Réglages iOS. Touchez pour ouvrir."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Gli interruttori sottostanti non avranno effetto finché non abiliti le notifiche per Lumoria in Impostazioni iOS. Tocca per aprire."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "下のスイッチは、iOSの設定でLumoriaの通知を有効にしないと反映されません。タップして開きます。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "아래 스위치는 iOS 설정에서 Lumoria 알림을 활성화해야 적용됩니다. 눌러서 여세요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "下列开关需先在 iOS 设置中开启 Lumoria 通知后才会生效。点按以打开。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "They create one ticket, that's all it takes.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Sie erstellen ein einziges Ticket – mehr braucht es nicht."
