    "This permanently removes your profile, tickets, memories, and invites. This cannot be undone.": {
      "comment": "A message displayed when the user is about to delete their account.",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Dadurch werden Ihr Profil, Ihre Tickets, Erinnerungen und Einladungen dauerhaft entfernt. Dies kann nicht rückgängig gemacht werden."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Deletes your profile, tickets, memories, and invites. This can’t be undone."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Esto eliminará de forma permanente tu perfil, boletos, recuerdos e invitaciones. No se puede deshacer."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cela supprime définitivement votre profil, vos billets, vos souvenirs et vos invitations. C'est irréversible."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Questa azione rimuove definitivamente profilo, biglietti, ricordi e inviti. Non si può annullare."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "プロフィール、チケット、思い出、招待が完全に削除されます。元に戻すことはできません。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "프로필, 티켓, 추억, 초대가 영구적으로 삭제됩니다. 되돌릴 수 없습니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "此操作将永久删除您的个人资料、票券、回忆和邀请，且无法撤销。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This stamps your account as an early adopter and opts you in for occasional research surveys. You can revoke any time from Settings.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Damit wird Ihr Konto als Early Adopter markiert und Sie nehmen an gelegentlichen Forschungsumfragen teil. Sie können dies jederzeit in den Einstellungen widerrufen."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Marks your account as an early adopter and opts you in for occasional research. Revoke anytime from Settings."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Esto marca tu cuenta como early adopter y te incluye en encuestas de investigación ocasionales. Puedes revocarlo en cualquier momento desde Ajustes."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cela marque votre compte comme early adopter et vous inscrit à des sondages de recherche occasionnels. Vous pouvez révoquer à tout moment depuis Réglages."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Questo marca il tuo account come early adopter e ti iscrive a sondaggi di ricerca occasionali. Puoi revocare in qualsiasi momento dalle Impostazioni."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "これによりアカウントがアーリーアダプターとして登録され、時折リサーチアンケートが届きます。いつでも「設定」から取り消せます。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "이 작업으로 계정이 얼리어답터로 표시되며 가끔 리서치 설문에 참여하게 됩니다. 설정에서 언제든 철회할 수 있습니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "此举将您的账户标记为早期使用者，并让您参与偶尔的研究问卷。您可以随时在“设置”中撤销。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This ticket is not part of a memory. Memories help you group tickets by trip, event, or place.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Dieses Ticket gehört noch zu keiner Erinnerung. Verbinde es mit einer, damit die Reise beisammen bleibt."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "This ticket isn’t part of any memory yet. Pair it with one to keep the trip together."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Este ticket aún no forma parte de ninguna memoria. Vincúlalo con una para mantener el viaje unido."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ce billet n’appartient encore à aucun souvenir. Associez-le pour garder le voyage ensemble."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Questo biglietto non fa ancora parte di nessun ricordo. Abbinalo a uno per tenere il viaggio unito."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "このチケットはまだどのメモリーにも属していません。ひとつに加えて、旅をひとまとめにしましょう。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "이 티켓은 아직 어떤 추억에도 속해 있지 않아요. 하나에 담아 여행을 한자리에 모아보세요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这张门票还不属于任何回忆。把它归入一段回忆，让整段旅程聚在一起。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
