    "Tickets are separated into categories. Pick a category to continue.": {
      "comment": "Tip to be displayed in the onboarding overlay when the user is selecting a ticket category.",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tickets sind in Kategorien unterteilt. Wählen Sie eine Kategorie, um fortzufahren."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tickets are sorted into categories. Pick one to continue."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Los boletos se separan en categorías. Elige una para continuar."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Les billets sont répartis en catégories. Choisissez-en une pour continuer."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "I biglietti sono suddivisi in categorie. Scegline una per continuare."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "チケットはカテゴリ別に分かれています。カテゴリを選んで進みます。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "티켓은 카테고리로 나뉩니다. 카테고리를 선택해 계속하세요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "票券按类别分组。选择一个类别以继续。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tickets arrange themselves into a two-column gallery. Vertical stubs pair up side by side; horizontal boarding passes take the full width. Tap any ticket to open it.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tickets ordnen sich in einer zweispaltigen Galerie an. Vertikale Stubs liegen nebeneinander; horizontale Bordkarten nehmen die volle Breite ein. Tippen Sie auf ein Ticket, um es zu öffnen."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tickets land in a two-column gallery. Vertical stubs pair up; horizontal boarding passes take the full width. Tap any to open."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Los boletos se organizan en una galería de dos columnas. Los stubs verticales se emparejan; las tarjetas de embarque horizontales ocupan todo el ancho. Toca cualquier boleto para abrirlo."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Les billets s'organisent en galerie à deux colonnes. Les souches verticales se placent côte à côte ; les cartes d'embarquement horizontales prennent toute la largeur. Touchez un billet pour l'ouvrir."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "I biglietti si dispongono in una galleria a due colonne. Le matrici verticali si affiancano, mentre le carte d'imbarco orizzontali occupano tutta la larghezza. Tocca un biglietto per aprirlo."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "チケットは2列のギャラリーに整列します。縦型のスタブは2枚並び、横型の搭乗券は幅いっぱいに表示されます。タップで開きます。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "티켓은 2단 갤러리로 정리됩니다. 세로 스텁은 나란히 배치되고, 가로 탑승권은 전체 너비를 차지합니다. 티켓을 누르면 열립니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "票券以双列画廊呈现。竖向票根并排放置，横向登机牌占满整宽。点按任意票券即可打开。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
