    "You joined Lumoria and created your first ticket with the invitation link from your friend. You can now unlock an additional benefit on Lumoria.": {
      "comment": "A body copy for the referree reward sheet.",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Sie sind Lumoria über den Einladungslink Ihres Freundes beigetreten und haben Ihr erstes Ticket erstellt. Sie können nun einen zusätzlichen Vorteil auf Lumoria freischalten."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "You joined through a friend’s invite and saved your first ticket. Pick a bonus to unlock."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Te has unido a Lumoria y has creado tu primer boleto con el enlace de invitación de tu amigo. Ya puedes desbloquear un beneficio adicional en Lumoria."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Vous avez rejoint Lumoria et créé votre premier billet via le lien d'invitation de votre ami. Vous pouvez maintenant débloquer un avantage supplémentaire sur Lumoria."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Sei entrato in Lumoria e hai creato il tuo primo biglietto con il link di invito del tuo amico. Ora puoi sbloccare un vantaggio aggiuntivo su Lumoria."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "友達からの招待リンクでLumoriaに参加し、最初のチケットを作成しました。ここでLumoriaの追加特典を解放できます。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "친구의 초대 링크로 Lumoria에 가입해 첫 티켓을 만들었습니다. 이제 Lumoria의 추가 혜택을 잠금 해제할 수 있습니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "你通过朋友的邀请链接加入 Lumoria 并创建了第一张票券。现在你可以在 Lumoria 上解锁额外福利。"
          }
        }
